OL,3,CMan stung more than 150 times after
OL,4,Cwasps attack and follow him into home
OL,6,FA man was attacked by a swarm of wasps
OL,7,Fwho followed him into his home.
OL,9,FAndrew Powell, from Brecon, was stung
OL,10,Fmore than 150 times by wasps after
OL,11,Fthey invaded his home at the weekend.
OL,13,FHe was outside in the garden to feed
OL,14,Fhis chickens when a swarm of wasps
OL,15,Fstung him.
OL,17,FHis bungalow backs on to farmers' land
OL,18,Fand he believes the wasps' nest was
OL,19,Fdisturbed by a combine harvester.
