OL,3,CMan stung more than 150 times after
OL,4,Cwasps attack and follow him into home
OL,6,FMr Powell ran into his home to jump in
OL,7,Fthe shower after all of his stings,
OL,8,Fbut hundreds of wasps followed him
OL,9,Finside.
OL,11,FHe said: "Suddenly there was a swarm
OL,12,Fof wasps and they came from nowhere
OL,13,Fand they came all around me.
OL,15,F"So, I turned and ran into the house
OL,16,Fup to the kitchen and into the
OL,17,Fbathroom.
OL,19,F"I put the shower on and by that time
OL,20,Fmy wife said that I was absolutely
OL,21,Fcovered in wasps.
