OL,4,Cwasps attack and follow him into home
OL,6,F"So, I put the shower on and I was
OL,7,Ftrying to get the wasps off me and my
OL,8,Fwife was throwing jugs of water over
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,F"They got into my shorts and my wife
OL,12,Fgot stung three or four times and the
OL,13,Fneighbour came after hearing the
OL,14,Fcommotion.
OL,16,F"She got stung on her face."
