OL,3,CMan stung more than 150 times after
OL,4,Cwasps attack and follow him into home
OL,6,FHe phoned his friend Richard Hall who
OL,7,Flives a mile away, who drove to
OL,8,Fcollect him and take him to Brecon War
OL,9,FMemorial Hospital's minor injuries
OL,10,Funit (MIU).
OL,12,FBy the time Richard got to Andrew's
OL,13,Fhome, he was starting to lose
OL,14,Fconsciousness.
OL,16,FRichard said he pre-alerted the MIU
OL,17,Fthat he was bringing Andrew in his
OL,18,Fcar, and said he also phoned 999 who
OL,19,Ftold him to pull over and wait for an
OL,20,Fambulance.
