OL,3,CMan stung more than 150 times after
OL,4,Cwasps attack and follow him into home
OL,6,FBut Richard headed straight to the MIU
OL,7,Fand asked the ambulance to meet him
OL,8,Fthere.
OL,10,FBy the time he got to the MIU, Andrew
OL,11,Fwas in and out of consciousness.
OL,13,FThe MIU nurses gave Andrew adrenaline
OL,14,Fand morphine.
OL,16,FThe pair were told if this
OL,17,Fintervention was given even 10 minutes
OL,18,Flater, Andrew could have died.
