OL,6,FThe minor injuries unit at Brecon War
OL,7,FMemorial Hospital is currently open 24
OL,8,Fhours a day, but the health board says
OL,9,Fnot enough people are using it at
OL,10,Fnight when it's already a struggle to
OL,11,Fstaff the department.
OL,13,FSo it wants to reduce those hours to
OL,14,F12 a day.
OL,16,FBut in a rural area where alternatives
OL,17,Fcan be far away, those plans are
OL,18,Fcausing concern.
