OL,3,CMan stung more than 150 times after
OL,4,Cwasps attack and follow him into home
OL,6,FKate Wright, medical director for
OL,7,FPowys Teaching Health Board, said:
OL,8,F"Our current service unfortunately has
OL,9,Ffaced difficulty in staffing.
OL,11,F"We've had to close overnight on short
OL,12,Fnotice. What that means is that our
OL,13,Fservice hasn't been reliable."
OL,15,FBut more than 1,300 people have signed
OL,16,Fa petition against the move and while
OL,17,Fthe unit is not designed to deal with
OL,18,Femergencies, Andrew's alternative was
OL,19,Fan A&E more than 30 miles away.
